I'm running into some trouble in my personal life right now, so I might have 
a bit of an irregular posting rate. I'll either post obsessively to get away 
from my life or a bit less than ussual cause I got so many things I need to 
take care of. Anyways, please be patient for me to reply, I'll do the best I 
can.

::Zardus/Havoc/Repressor::

Zardus' eyes narrow, listening to Lady Hawk's words.

"You are in no position to make demands," he says, motioning to Repressor. 
The bot takes a step back, out of Lady Hawk's reach, and aims a good sized 
gun at her. Zardus looks back to Lady Hawk, "Now, what were you doing to 
Squizzy?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Havoc stops, nearing the flying portions of the Alliance base. For some 
reason they had slowed, continuing ahead slowly. He activates his internal 
computers, tapping into the computer of one of the shuttles.

He nods, looking through the info he got back. The cargo section was a bit 
too heavy for the shuttle carrying it, so they had to slow for now. Another 
shuttle from the Iron Fist was on its way to soon help.

He sighs, flying ahead to the Iron Fist.
